Interface iStationData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    baseCDMClass, Grid, Profile, Section, TimeSeries, TimeSeriesProfile, Trajectory

    public interface iStationData
    Interface used for the CDM Feature Types Provides functional interface for handling various feature type datasets in providing information for Get Capabilities and Get Observation requests.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    abird
